<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10469061>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Three species in family Atrochidae. A. Cupelopagis vorax (Leidy, 1857), side view; insert dorsal view. B. Two individuals of Acyclus inquietus Leidy, 1882 removed from a colony of S. socialis. C. Atrochus tentaculatus Wierzejski, 1893. (C. After Wierzejski, 1893). Symbols: B = body; F = foot; I = infundibulum; G = gelatinous matrix; S = substratum. Bars ~1000 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10469061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

